									style="margin-left: 10px; color: green; display: none;">已经自动填充患者信息</span></td>
							</tr>
							<tr height="40" valign="bottom">
								<!-- <td width="80" style="line-height:30px;">条形码</td>
	                            <td width="310"><input type="text" class="input14" id="adiconBarcode"/></td> -->
